<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>429 - 请求过于频繁</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div class="text-center p-10 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-md w-full">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-purple-500 m-0">429</h1>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 my-5">请求过于频繁</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">您的请求次数已超过限制，请稍后再试。</p>

        {% if retry_after %}
        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded p-4 mb-4">
            <p class="text-purple-800 text-sm">
                请在 <span class="font-bold" id="countdown">{{ retry_after }}</span> 秒后重试
            </p>
        </div>
        <script>
            let seconds = {{ retry_after }};
            const countdown = document.getElementById('countdown');
            const timer = setInterval(() => {
                seconds--;
                countdown.textContent = seconds;
                if (seconds <= 0) {
                    clearInterval(timer);
                    location.reload();
                }
            }, 1000);
        </script>
        {% endif %}

        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-8">为了保护服务器资源，我们限制了请求频率。感谢您的理解！</p>

        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-blue-500 text-white no-underline rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300">返回首页</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
